Here is the translation:

Came a traveler's cloud, the Lord of Harishena; 
Seven times was it pleasant, the Shaka tree's branches entwined rudely.

Here is the translation:

Stayed stayed sleepiness came, makes own self make ready;
Themselves brings extra love, cuts off the door and blocks the way.

Here is the translation:

When I was playing with life, I knew my own self; 
I made myself dance to beautiful Surval, following the beat of Zageshki Jamanee.

Here is the translation:

Playful love rejoices in colorful play, thieves steal away quietly; 
The person who does what they do will be done to them, one will see oneself after a long time without end.

Here is the translation:

Come, Govind, seated on a high throne; 
Tell Munivrin to bring worship; 
After that, saints brought good worship; 
And took out Keshar Chandna.

Here is the translation:

The great king has come and sat on the stage, saying listen to my royal orders; 
Bring color with your hands, whatever people are living in that place, put it on their heads.

Here is the translation:

Sorrow's color has been filled in this place, we two have played a game and got drunk with joy; 
After that, friends became aware, got alert, I will watch my playful game with God.

Keep saints playing, keep playing to play; 
Let others enjoy eating to eat; 
Let's go together on the river, as I said with a gesture of my hand.
